<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <% include ./head %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include nav %>
    <div class="container">
      <% include ./banner %>
      <div
        class="row font-mine color-crtext cr-padding-main em-1-1 text-center justify-content-center"
      >
        <p>
          Code riddler is a fun platform for solving riddles about software ecosystem
           in general. It contains challenging riddles for you to
          solve and find the answers. <br /><br />
          Code riddler is in BETA, meaning you'll find some bugs along the way.
          You can
          <a
            href="https://github.com/codekidX/code_riddler/issues"
            target="_blank"
            class="cr-link"
            >report bugs
          </a>
          /
          <a
            href="https://github.com/codekidX/code_riddler/issues/new"
            target="_blank"
            class="cr-link"
            >share your ideas</a
          >
          to make it more fun platform.

          <br /><br />
          Have any riddles in mind ?
          <br />
          <span class="cr-link" onclick="changeLocation('/submit')"
            >Submit your riddle here</span
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
      <% if (loggedIn) { %>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <button
          onclick="changeLocation('/riddles')"
          class="cr-button-small color-crtext font-mine"
        >
          Solve
        </button>
      </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="row justify-content-center text-center font-mine color-crtext">
            <p>Login to solve riddles and save your points.</p>
        </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/login/oauth/authorize?client_id=a3efd738d9044319090d"
        >
          <button
            id="loginButton"
            class="cr-button-small color-crtext font-mine mar-l-1"
          >
            Login with Github
          </button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <% } %>
      <!-- <div class="mar-t-4 mar-b-4">
        <hr />
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <p class="font-mine-bold em-1-3 color-crtext ">Leaderboards</p>
      </div> -->
      <% include footer %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
